title: China Hacked US Email Systems
description:
In this video I discuss how a Chinese threat actor was able to successfully breach the email systems of several US and European government and private sector organizations through a flaw in Microsoft's email service and how popular tax prep services were sending customer to Facebook through Meta pixel.
